nodes.text: Lee-Chee Mukmuk was a yellow Kowakian monkey-lizard who was seen in Slum district G17 alongside two Weequay criminals during the Clone Wars. The Kowakian saw the lightsaber of Ahsoka Tano when the young Togruta Padawan and her Master, Anakin Skywalker were looking for the Weequay criminal Car Affa.

Lee-Chee Mukmuk, credited as "Muk Muk Monkey", was voiced by Jaime King, who also voiced Cassie Cryar in "Lightsaber Lost", an episode of Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series. King additionally voiced Aurra Sing in the series.
